sentence: Wyoming Republican Party leaders moved to allow the Republican National Committee to support Harriet Hageman, who has been endorsed by former President Donald Trump in her primary run against Rep. Liz Cheney, on a financial basis.
author: Emily Brooks
title: Wyoming GOP move to allow RNC to fund Cheney challenger spurs outrage
